  "2162020": {
    "name": "末光",
    "steam_appid": 2162020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/4eaa7fab2b87095def89fe9311395ffe.poster.avif?t=1756799953\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/4eaa7fab2b87095def89fe9311395ffe.webm?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/4eaa7fab2b87095def89fe9311395ffe.mp4?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《末光》是一款令人身临其境的动作冒险游戏，背景设定在一个充满了腐化和阴影的无言而梦幻的世界。你是一缕初生的光，踏上一段将自己从周围的阴影中解放出来的自我救赎之路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/49f8438af8a026c305127a22146a8559.poster.avif?t=1756799953\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/49f8438af8a026c305127a22146a8559.webm?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/49f8438af8a026c305127a22146a8559.mp4?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>《末光》的主要特点：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 与被情绪扭曲的可爱生物进行战斗，改变颜色以抵御它们的攻击。<br></li><li> 无需对白，体验一场艺术般情绪升华的电影化游戏体验。<br></li><li> 在《末光》中探索破碎大陆，从发光的森林到峡谷、洞穴，以及令人举目茫然的迷雾之地。<br></li><li> 游戏配乐是由 Austin Wintory 创作的原声音乐，氛围感极强，令人流连忘返。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/959de9ead50ec14249751985776351eb.poster.avif?t=1756799953\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/959de9ead50ec14249751985776351eb.webm?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/959de9ead50ec14249751985776351eb.mp4?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恢复你的光芒</h2>玩家将扮演一团被阴影撕裂的新生火焰。在一个充满敌意的世界中不断前行，一路抵抗心魔，帮助沿途的各种生物，借此来恢复自身的光芒。当你的光芒变亮时可解锁新的能力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/3a2210638c66ea4998499161337e2186.poster.avif?t=1756799953\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/3a2210638c66ea4998499161337e2186.webm?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/3a2210638c66ea4998499161337e2186.mp4?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >安抚你的敌人</h2>找到腐化的兄弟姐妹，他们每个人都被特定的情绪影响而变得扭曲。与这些怪物战斗，安抚舒缓它们的情绪。同时直面阻碍你前进的心魔。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/e4bde28d7ced2f5ba4d0142ac722ce74.poster.avif?t=1756799953\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/e4bde28d7ced2f5ba4d0142ac722ce74.webm?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/e4bde28d7ced2f5ba4d0142ac722ce74.mp4?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通过改变颜色进行战斗</h2>在流畅而爽快的战斗中面对被阴影撕裂的各种生物。你需要在蓝色和橙色之间切换来与怪物的颜色匹配，从而抵御它们的攻击，并通过华丽的终结技能打败它们。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/7feeb9791b871661bd3ae22a9860633b.poster.avif?t=1756799953\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/7feeb9791b871661bd3ae22a9860633b.webm?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162020/extras/7feeb9791b871661bd3ae22a9860633b.mp4?t=1756799953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
